'desc': [u'

Chicco Zanza No Wipes (15 Pieces) Price: Rs.269

Wet wipes can be used for cleansing your tiny tot's skin after nappy change or even while travelling. The Chicco Zanza No Wipes are wet wipes that have been designed and created to keep your bundle of joy's skin protected. These Wet Wipes from Chicco have Citronella and Indian Lilac infused into them. The extracts of these plants have antibacterial and antiseptic properties that will help in safeguarding your baby's skin against such microorganisms. Indian Lilac also commonly known as Neem is good in treating various skin ailments and thus keeping the skin healthy.

The Zanza No Wipes from Chicco has a sweet fragrance that will linger on your and your little angel's skin after using this wipe. Your baby's skin will feel velvety soft and will have no graces of any dirt or excess oil after it is wiped clean by the Chicco Wet Wipes. These skin friendly Wet Wipes are suitable even for a newborn's fragile skin. Give your little darling the best cleansing experience with this Chicco Zanzo No Wipes that will soften and moisturize the skin.
